icial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/SCDM/111%2c%e8%a8%b4%2c319%2c20220825%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"SCDM,111,訴,319,20220825,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"訴","JNO":"319","JDATE":"20220825","JTITLE":"違反槍砲彈藥刀械管制條例"}